        <item>
            <title>【評測】Denon PerL Pro 純白無線藍牙耳機　AI 度身訂做個人最佳 EQ 比例 + 高頻有誠意</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/denon-perl-pro-white/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=denon-perl-pro-white</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/denon-perl-pro-white/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:15:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Denon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Denon PerL Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[真無線藍牙耳機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1243510</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本高級音響品牌 Denon 所屬的 Sound United 早年被美國醫療科技公司 Masimo 收購，推出新一代高級真無線藍牙耳機。除了機身設計特別，採用鑊型設計外，其更採用了 Masimo 的醫學科技，運用 AI 為用家度身訂做最佳 EQ 比例。近日更推出了全新純白色版供用家選擇。下面就讓小編和大家分享一下 Denon PerL Pro 的聽後感吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09444-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09444-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09444.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09514-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09514-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09514.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><h2></h2><h2>設計質感十足　反光外圈彰顯高級地位</h2><p>先從外觀説起，Denon PerL Pro 採用磨砂白色機身，可能是為了收納 10 mm 大單元，耳機外殼比市面上的真無線藍牙耳機更大。耳機採用圓盤形設計，磨砂白色機身配以反光外圈點綴，質感十足。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09447-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09447-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09447.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PerL Pro 耳機以反光外圈點綴，高級感十足</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09491-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09491-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09491.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲或因耳機內有 10 mm 單元， Denon PerL Pro 比一般耳機更大</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09474-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09474-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09474.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲充電盒上有 DENON 字樣</p><h2>4 款大小耳膠 +記憶耳棉　新增 XS 尺碼</h2><p>純白 Denon PerL Pro 隨機附贈「XS、S、M、L」 4 個尺碼的耳膠，與先前黑色版本相比增加了「XS」選項，相信是為了照顧耳洞較小的用家。另外亦附有專為運動用家而設的 「Wing Attachment」，以鞏固耳機。除此之外 Denon 亦照顧到想進一步提升隔音朋友，隨機亦附贈一對記憶耳綿，任君選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09451-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09451-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09451.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲純白版本除了加入 XS 耳膠外，亦將 USB-A 接口改為 USB-C，另外隨附轉接頭</p><p>Denon PerL Pro 雖然看起來很「掗拃」，但可能因為其單邊重量僅有 8 g，小編實際試戴感受又不太覺得有負擔。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09494-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09494-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09494-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看起來很大，但實際佩戴不會感覺到</p><h2>3 收音咪 + 1 骨傳導咪　通話清晰隔絕背景音</h2><p>Denon PerL Pro 耳機每邊設有 4 個收音咪，其中一個更為骨傳導咪，用家即使在鬧市中使用 Denon PerL Pro 通話亦未見有嘈雜聲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243575" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09456-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09456-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09456.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳機背設多個收音 mic</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09463-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09463-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09463.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09462-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09462-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09462.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>高音嘹亮　適合聽女聲</h2><p>作為一款高階真無線藍牙耳機，Denon PerL Pro 配有 aptX 編碼，滿足對音質有要求的用家。以下小編就試用 Qualcomm aptX Adaptive 連接 Denon PerL Pro，試聽幾首歌。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183478" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-248x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-248x580.png 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-385x900.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157.png 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-181157-658x1536.png 658w" alt="" width="248" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用 aptX Adaptive 連接</p><p>Denon PerL Pro 女聲嘹亮清晰，小編試用這對真無線藍牙耳機播放房東的貓《你是我最愚蠢的一次浪漫》，女主音的温柔聲音猶在耳邊，整體聽感不會覺得尖鋭，反而有一種軟綿綿的感覺；背景結他和沙鎚伴奏部份亦非常認真，不會馬虎了事。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-248x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-248x580.png 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-385x900.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131.png 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184131-658x1536.png 658w" alt="" width="248" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲房東的貓《你是我最愚蠢的一次浪漫》</p><p>小編之後亦試聽了陳蕾《 娛樂人生》，歌曲節拍感強勁之餘亦不會含糊交帶女聲部分，副歌爆發位更令小編感到驚艷。PerL Pro 高頻表現不俗，但低音部分較為失望。幸而使用 Denon Headphone App 以 AI 調校 EQ 後加上其 Immersion Mode 的話，低音下潛力聽起來會更強烈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-248x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 248px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-248x580.png 248w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-385x900.png 385w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053.png 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot_20230803-184053-658x1536.png 658w" alt="" width="248" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陳蕾《娛樂人生》</p><h2>醫療級科技收集用家耳蝸結構　AI 度身訂做 EQ</h2><p>美國醫療科技公司 Masimo 收購 Denon 後，加入了專利醫療級聲學分析技術 「Masimo AAT 自適應聲學技術」（Masimo Adaptive Acoustic Technology，AAT）。用家只需下載「Denon Headphones」應用程式，簡單註冊帳户，之後戴好耳機，AAT 就會自動分析你的內耳結構，並利用 Denon Headphones 專用 App 的 AI 為你度身訂做獨一無二專屬 EQ，提供真正定製的個人化聲音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09520-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09520-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09520.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>整個測試非常簡單，用家先要找一個安靜的地方，再連接耳筒，然後開啟「Denon Headphone」應用程式，再按程式的指示照做就行。不過要注意的是，應用程式評估你耳朵內部時會發出尖鋭的聲音，對高頻聲音敏感的朋友就要留意一下了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1182596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y-268x580.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555570_y.jpg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1182593" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y-268x580.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/photo_6213088171747555571_y.jpg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲起始頁面</p><p>完成評估後，AI 會為你繪製一個靈敏度頻譜圖，圖中 12 點方向是低頻，順時針方向一直轉下去音頻就愈高，Denon 的 AI 會為你繪製你專屬的耳朵頻道，再以 EQ 補足音樂播放效果。藍色圈圈部分代表標準頻譜，粉紅色部分就是 Denon AI 偵測出你的聽力量頻譜。拿小編的靈敏度頻譜圖作例子，小編在聽低中頻方面較不靈敏，高頻方面則非常敏感。Denon Headphone App 就按照檢測結果加強中低頻的 EQ，讓小編可以聽到更多這個頻譜的聲音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-268x580.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-416x900.jpeg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050.jpeg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲起始頁面</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1183682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1-268x580.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1-416x900.jpeg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/photo1691153050-1.jpeg 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小編的左右耳評測結果</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09478-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09478-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09478.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>總結：女聲不含糊　AI EQ 有巧思</h2><p>Denon PerL Pro 整體使用體驗不俗，雖然外觀看起來有點大，但得益於其 8 g 蠅量級重量，實際佩戴體驗不會讓用家感受到其存在。音色方面，耳機不負 Denon 之名，所有細節清楚交代之餘，女聲亦毫不含糊。除此以外，Masimo 帶來的「Masimo AAT 自適應聲學技術」亦非常有誠意，要試盡耳機的話真的要試玩這個 AI。惟一要彈的就是低頻部分，小編覺得要靠 EQ 打救。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/denon-perl-pro-white/mobile-music/headphones/">【評測】Denon PerL Pro 純白無線藍牙耳機　AI 度身訂做個人最佳 EQ 比例 + 高頻有誠意</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
