            <title>警隊訓練引入 Mixed Reality 技術，模擬不同環境供 PTU 作戰術訓練</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/hkpolice-mr-training-system/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hkpolice-mr-training-system</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/hkpolice-mr-training-system/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:00:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ar]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[混合實境]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1243532</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">警察機動部隊（PTU）總部研究及發展科年初引入混合實境（Mixed Reality）技術，務求加強訓練效果。根據《星島》報道，這個混合實境結合了虛擬實境（VR）與擴增實境（AR）的技術，以感知技術、顯示技術、空間映射等科技結合虛擬與真實物件，使受訓人員可透過頭戴式顯示器與虛擬物體和真實環境互動，並在模擬的各種環境中進行戰術訓練。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243533" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1_2-694x463.jpeg" alt="警隊「混合實境」技術" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1_2-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1_2.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星島</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243543 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2_3-694x463.jpeg" alt="警隊「混合實境」技術" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2_3-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2_3.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星島</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1243544 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/7_2-694x463.jpeg" alt="警隊「混合實境」技術" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/7_2-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/7_2.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星島</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">警察機動部隊總部研究及發展科總督察鄭偉文，解釋受訓人員所佩戴的開放式頭戴顯示器裝有紅外線傳感器偵測感知和定位，配備的「模擬槍」同樣裝有紅外線傳感器能偵測受訓人員的瞄準動作和方向。MR 訓練系統安置於地上的「被動式定位方塊」將場上人員的定位訊號接收，中央處理系統能實時顯示訓練情況，受訓人員於整個場景的位置、方向，槍的指向等都能展示，並記錄於系統中。受訓人員以第一人稱視角在模擬場景中執行任務，與隊友溝通並制定戰術，制服匪徒和救出人質。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">MR 訓練系統可配合各種需要模擬出不同的場景，訓練受訓人員於不同情況下的應對能力。凌子傑警司表示整個 MR 訓練系統都會精確地記錄過程，可用作數據分析，錄像回放亦有助受訓人員回顧整個訓練，提升訓練的質素。郭家俊高級警司指出 MR 訓練系統中極高像真度的沉浸式體驗，能令受訓人員訓練時更投入，為整個訓練的效果大大提升。</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2005138/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-PTU%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%A2%83-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83-%E5%8A%A9%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B2%BE%E7%9B%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%B2%BE?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR0swAB425v8LCzoXRJExakIBHvPfiSk7Z_bJzmHCDmR8G6VhTQYl_fqalo_aem_rysa03S-sLbDSPxB133l7g">星島</a></span></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/12/htc-u24-pro/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">HTC 發佈新手機 U24 Pro     支援 VIVE XR Elite VR 裝置+ AI 拍照功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/18/lg-display-vr-oledos-10000nits/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">LG Display VR 專屬屏幕，高達 10,000nits 亮度</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/17/hkpolice-mr-training-system/fun-tech/">警隊訓練引入 Mixed Reality 技術，模擬不同環境供 PTU 作戰術訓練</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
